Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.82,0:00:53.57,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,Yuzuka wakes up at six every morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.95,0:00:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.99,0:01:00.83,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,She pays attention in class \Nand has excellent grades.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.29,0:01:04.33,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,She carries out all of her chores perfectly.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.96,0:01:09.50,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,She refuses to take a bath with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:10.17,0:01:14.26,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,Honestly, it's absolutely ridiculous\N for a magical girl not to do so.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.05,0:01:17.55,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,She doesn't like being a magical girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.05,0:01:20.22,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,She's an unusual magical girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:22.85,0:01:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yuzuka.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.23,0:01:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.48,0:01:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you happy you became a magical girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.19,0:01:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ignoring me?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.65,0:01:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.19,0:01:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The... beach?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.24,0:01:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,One of my father's friends \Ninvited me to their beach house.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.16,0:01:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to come with me?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.08,0:01:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A beach house, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.46,0:01:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds great!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.62,0:01:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It is!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.33,0:01:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.96,0:01:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a private beach!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.84,0:01:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's more than just a house.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.84,0:01:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently only people staying \Nat the hotel there can visit.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.55,0:01:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The beach...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.68,0:02:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Yuzuka-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.43,0:02:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have an adventure!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.85,0:02:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Yuzuka.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.52,0:02:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We can make great summer memories.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.69,0:02:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.86,0:02:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.66,0:02:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the beach!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.91,0:02:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The blue is so deep, it could suck you in!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.33,0:02:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does Shiori-chan have a bomb on her, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.92,0:02:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So hot...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.34,0:02:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I took so long.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.35,0:02:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.35,0:02:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have just \Ntransformed into your swimsuit.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.60,0:02:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.39,0:02:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Though your school swimsuit is nice, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.65,0:02:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty stimulating in itself.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.66,0:02:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mafuyu-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.40,0:02:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't say I disagree.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.11,0:02:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Not you too, Chiya-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.70,0:03:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A little more to the right.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.45,0:03:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.95,0:03:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,To the right. Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.41,0:03:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.00,0:03:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.67,0:03:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Strike!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.59,0:03:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotten pretty good.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.88,0:03:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.14,0:03:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.93,0:03:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuzuka-chan, you should swim with us, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.85,0:03:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a tough one to crack.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.40,0:03:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be a good chance for her to get used to her swimsuit, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.98,0:03:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess we'll just have to drag her out here.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.32,0:03:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I get to be the one to take off her jacket.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.32,0:03:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's up?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.87,0:03:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm coming.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.76,0:04:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,To be continued!
